items.headline: Panthers at Islanders preview
items.subhead: Montembeault expected to start for Florida; New York has lost three of first four
items.seoTitle: Florida Panthers New York Islanders game preview
items.seoDescription: Sam Montembeault is expected to make his first start of the season for the Florida Panthers against the New York Islanders at Nassau Coliseum on Saturday.
items.seoKeywords: Florida Panthers, New York Islanders, game preview, NHL, hockey, October 12, Sam Montembeault
items.preview:
PANTHERS (1-2-1) at ISLANDERS (1-3-0)

7 p.m. ET; MSG+, FS-F, NHL.TV

 

The Game 

Sam Montembeault is expected to make his first start of the season for the Florida Panthers against the New York Islanders at Nassau Coliseum on Saturday.

items.headline: Varlamov sparks Islanders in shootout win against Panthers
items.subhead: Makes 35 saves for first victory with New York; Florida drops third straight
items.seoTitle: Florida Panthers New York Islanders game recap
items.seoDescription: UNIONDALE, N.Y. -- Semyon Varlamov made 35 saves and three more in the shootout for his first win with the New York Islanders, 3-2 against the Florida Panthers at Nassau Coliseum on Saturday.
items.seoKeywords: Florida Panthers, New York Islanders, game recap, NHL, hockey, news, October 12
